data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Vancleave, Mississippi! Nestled on a spacious 2-acre lot, this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bath residence boasts both comfort and style. From the cozy gas fireplace to the picturesque surroundings.The open-concept living area is a true focal point of the home, complete with a gas fireplace that sets the perfect ambiance for cozy evenings with loved ones. The kitchen is open to the the living room and also is next to the large laundry area. The 3 bedrooms are a great size and 2 of the bedrooms have  walk in closets. This home also features a room that can be used as an office, game room or a 4th bedroom.  The 2-acre lot offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities, gardening, creating your own peaceful oasis and ensures privacy from neighbors.
